/** @jsxImportSource @emotion/react */
import { css } from '@emotion/react';

export const headerContainer = css({
    width: '100%',
    textAlign: 'center',
    padding: '20px',
    boxSizing: 'border-box',
    position: 'fixed',
    height: 90,
    backgroundColor: '#FFF',
    top: 0,
    '-webkit-box-shadow': '0px 10px 10px 0px rgba(176,174,176,0.2)',
    'box-shadow': '0px 10px 10px 0px rgba(176,174,176,0.2)',
})
